KoPrivateGPT.benchmark.retrieval.main module

KoPrivateGPT.benchmark.retrieval.main.basic_retrieval_evaluation(qrels: Dict[str, Dict[str, int]], results: Dict[str, Dict[str, float]], k_values: List[int]) → List[dict[str, float]]
Parameters:

  • qrels – The qrels file as a dictionary. Dict[query_id, Dict[doc_id, relevance]]

  • results – The results file as a dictionary. Dict[query_id, Dict[doc_id, score]]

K_values:

The k values for which the evaluation should be done. List[int]

results doc_id can be different from the doc_id in the qrels file.
